headline: 10 Dividend Stocks That Look Better Than Bonds
summary: As Treasury yields fall, dividend stocks with higher payouts and room to maintain them are becoming an appealing bond alternative.

headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 We Turn Down
summary: While the S&P 500 (^GSPC) includes industry leaders, not every stock in the index is a winner. Some companies are past their prime, weighed down by poor execution, weak financials, or structural headwinds.
